      <section class="ui piled segment">
        <h3 class="news">News</h3>

        <div class="ui celled list">
          <div class="item news-items">
              <div class="content news-content">
              <div class="header">16 january 2018</div>
              I attended the last Montreal.rb meetup. It was my first time there !
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item news-items">
            <div class="content news-content">
              <div class="header">05 january 2018</div>
              I just began looking for a job ~~ ! Wish me good luck.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item news-items">
              <div class="content news-content">
              <div class="header">December 2017</div>
              I finished my reproduction of the New York Times page in HTML/CSS.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </section>
    </div>
</div>
</main>
